<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Aqua AI | Multi-Model AI Chatbot</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Aqua AI is a powerful multi-model AI chatbot by Aquiplex. Generate content, code, ideas, and more using advanced AI models in one place.">

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #020617;
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(30px, 7vw, 48px);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #a78bfa);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: clamp(15px, 3vw, 18px);
      color: #94a3b8;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 25px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #6366f1);
      color: white;
      padding: 13px 24px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .cta-btn:hover {
      opacity: 0.85;
    }

    /* ── Sections ── */
    .section {
      margin-top: 70px;
      padding: 0 4px;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(20px, 4.5vw, 28px);
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .section p {
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: clamp(14px, 2.5vw, 16px);
    }

    /* ── Grid ── */
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(230px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #0f172a;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #1e293b;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      border-color: #6366f1;
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(15px, 3vw, 17px);
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .card a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 12px;
      color: #38bdf8;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .card a:hover {
      color: #a78bfa;
    }

    /* ── Steps ── */
    .steps {
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .step {
      color: #cbd5f5;
      font-size: clamp(14px, 2.5vw, 16px);
      padding: 12px 16px;
      background: #0f172a;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #1e293b;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #38bdf8;
    }

    /* ── Explore section below container ── */
    .explore-section {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 60px auto 0;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .explore-section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 26px);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* ── Mobile ── */
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        padding: 30px 16px;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 40px 16px;
      }

      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .section {
        margin-top: 50px;
      }

      .section[style*="text-align:center"] .cta-btn {
        display: block;
        max-width: 260px;
        margin: 20px auto 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .explore-section {
        padding: 0 16px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <%- include("partials/every") %>

  <div class="container">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Aqua AI</h1>
      <p>
        A powerful multi-model AI chatbot that helps you create, build, and solve anything—
        from content and code to ideas and projects.
      </p>
      <a href="/chatbot" class="cta-btn">Try Aqua AI →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- WHAT IS -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>What is Aqua AI?</h2>
      <p>
        Aqua AI is an advanced AI chatbot developed by Aquiplex that combines multiple AI models
        into one unified system. It allows users to generate content, solve problems, write code,
        and build ideas faster using intelligent AI assistance.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FEATURES -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>What Can You Do with Aqua AI?</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card"><h3>✍️ Generate Content</h3><p>Create blogs, captions, scripts, and more instantly.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>💻 Write & Fix Code</h3><p>Get help with coding, debugging, and development tasks.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>🚀 Build Ideas</h3><p>Turn ideas into structured plans and real outputs.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>🧠 Learn Faster</h3><p>Understand concepts with clear explanations.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>🎨 Generate Images</h3><p>Create visuals and designs using AI.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>📊 Summarize & Research</h3><p>Break down complex information quickly.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>How to Use Aqua AI</h2>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">1. Enter your prompt or idea</div>
        <div class="step">2. Choose your task (content, code, etc.)</div>
        <div class="step">3. Get instant AI-generated results</div>
        <div class="step">4. Refine and improve outputs</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- DIFFERENCE -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>Why Aqua AI is Different</h2>
      <p>
        Unlike traditional chatbots, Aqua AI is built for <span class="highlight">execution</span>, not just conversation.
        It integrates multiple AI models and focuses on helping users actually build and create things.
      </p>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card"><h3>Multi-Model System</h3><p>Powered by multiple AI engines for better results.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Execution Focused</h3><p>Helps you create real outputs, not just answers.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>All-in-One Platform</h3><p>No need to switch between multiple tools.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- USE CASES -->
    <div class="section">
      <h2>Who is Aqua AI For?</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card"><h3>Students</h3><p>Learn faster, complete assignments, and explore ideas.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Creators</h3><p>Generate content, posts, and creative assets.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Developers</h3><p>Write, debug, and improve code efficiently.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Startup Founders</h3><p>Build ideas and MVPs quickly using AI.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FINAL CTA -->
    <div class="section" style="text-align:center;">
      <h2>Start Building with Aqua AI</h2>
      <p>Experience the future of AI-powered creation.</p>
      <a href="/chatbot" class="cta-btn">Launch Aqua AI →</a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- EXPLORE MORE -->
  <div class="explore-section">
    <h2>Explore More</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Aqua Project Engine</h3>
        <p>Turn AI ideas into real projects.</p>
        <a href="/aqua-project-engine">Explore →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>About Aquiplex</h3>
        <p>Understand the platform behind Aqua AI.</p>
        <a href="/about">Learn more →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <%- include("partials/footer") %>

</body>
</html>
